fields.name: White and turqouise Chandra, Moon catears with rhinestones and chain decoration
fields.description: These enchanting white catears is an upgrade of the “Luna” model and is called “Chandra”.They have a crescent moon made of turquoise glitter and clear swarovski crystals and rhinestones in three sizes. Even the backside is decorated with Swarovski crystals and rhinestones.They also have a decoration on the front made of thin silver colored chains, swarowski preals and silver bells that will rest on your forhead when wearing them.Being white they are part of the standard productline, you can also find them in black.

fields.name: Black and silver Chandra, Moon catears with rhinestones and chain decoration
fields.description: These enchanting black catears is an upgrade of the “Luna” model and is called “Chandra”. They have a crescent moon made of silver glitter and clear swarovski crystals and rhinestones in three sizes. Even the backside is decorated with Swarovski crystals and rhinestones. They also have a decoration on the front made of thin silver colored chains, swarowski preals and silver bells that will rest on your forhead when wearing them. You can also find them in white.

fields.name: “Catlady” necklace in quipu code with swarovski and malachite pearls
fields.description: This is a stylish ready-to-wear necklace that spells out the word “Catlady” in quipu code, and it is part of the summer collection. Check out the other Catlady-necklaces for other variations. This necklace have the color combo: * 3mm swarowski pearl: Scarab green, * 6mm semi-precious stone: Malachite. Each string with pearls reprecent a letter, and is attached to a thin chain that goes around the neck with a small lock on the back.

fields.name: “Catlady” necklace in ancient quipu code - Queen Edition. Clear bicone and amethyst
fields.description: This is an upgrade of the ready-to-wear Catlady-necklace! The Queen Edition is even more shiny and will surely draw attention to you. Instead of pearls 4mm swarvovski beads are used, and instead of metal pearls, big 8mm swarovski pearls are used. The 8mm pearls and the semi precious stone pearls also have silver colored bead caps for that extra luxurious finish. In sunlight the clear bicone beads looks like morning dew in a spider's web. This necklace have the color combo: * 4mm swarowski bicone: Clear,* 6mm semi-precious stone: Amethyst, * 8mm swarovski pearl: Burgundy

fields.name: Leopard printed cat ears with glitter and rhinestones
fields.description: Handmade, one-of-a-kind catears. Dare to bring out your inner cat with these pretty ears. The perfect accessory that will take your outfit to the next level. These catears have a leopard print made of glitter i various colors, and the backside have small rhinestones to match. The leo print is done by hand directly on the ear which make each ear different from the rest.

fields.name: Personalized name necklace in Quipu code (2-8 letters)
fields.description: Design a personal name-necklace in the ancient and mysterious quipu code! You can think of it like a morse code. The pearls positions on the strings follows a certain pattern and each string with pearls represent a letter. The letters are attached to a thin 1.8 mm silver colored chain that goes around the neck with a small spring lock on the back. All letters have a “base color” of 3 mm Swarovski pearls. The vowels have a 6 mm Stardust metal bead, and some of the consonants have 6 mm semi-precious stone pearls. All Qupiu necklaces comes with a Code Translation Card so you’ll know how to read it

fields.name: Luna cat ears with glitter moon, Swarovski crystals and pearl earring decor
fields.description: Handmade, one-of-a-kind catears.Dare to bring out your inner cat with these meow-gical ears. The perfect accessory that will take your outfit to the next level. This model is called “Luna” and is avaible i a varaity of colors. They have a glitter moon with swarowski crystals on the front, and they have an earring in each ear. The backside is plain.
